These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, techno, disco, d&b
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, italian, indonesian, american
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, jet-ski, boat, trike
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the trike is between the italian and the fan of trance##2
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the fan of disco##1
5. the canadian is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
6. the indonesian is on the right of the fan of techno##1
7. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | disco      | techno      | d&b    |
| Nationality   | american | canadian | italian | indonesian |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | trike       | boat     | quad-bike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, pumpkin, radish, asparagus
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, sudoku, magic-tricks, drawing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, western, animation, horror
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
2. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
6. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
7. the person eating radish is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Food          | apple     | asparagus     | pumpkin       | radish    |
| Hobby         | sudoku | magic-tricks   | video-games | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | horror    | animation | western    | crime        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, hot-chocolate, mirinda
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, spanish, french, australian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, volleyball, swimming
1. the spanish is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the french##3
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the argentine##3
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the french is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
7. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | 7up | tea  | hot-chocolate    | mirinda |
| Nationality   | french   | australian  | argentine  | spanish    |
| Sport         | biathlon    | swimming | basketball | volleyball  |

