.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, eggplant, grapes, nectarine
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, musical, epic, western
4 different pets are kept: horse, fish, hamster, bird
1. the owner of the fish is between the person watching musical movies and the person eating kale##2
2. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
4. the person eating grapes is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the horse is the person eating nectarine##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
7. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
8. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | grapes   | kale     | eggplant | nectarine |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | western | animation   | musical     |
| Pet           | bird | hamster      | fish     | horse       |

