.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, blueberry, grapefruit, cucumber
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, security-guard, bartender, electrician
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, animation, crime, family
1. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3
3. the bartender is the person watching spy movies##1
4. the engineer is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating blueberry##2
5. the bartender is on the right of the electrician##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
7. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3
8. the person eating grapefruit is the person watching crime movies##1
9. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person eating cucumber##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | grapefruit      | cucumber | blueberry      | potato |
| Job           | security-guard | engineer | electrician | bartender   |
| Movie-Genre   | crime    | family   | animation     | spy   |

