.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, engineer, chef, electrician
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, blues, house
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, basketball, rugby, cycling
1. the person who's sport is basketball is the librarian##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is the fan of house##1
3. the librarian is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
5. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
6. the chef is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the engineer is on the right of the fan of folk##1
8. the engineer is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Job           | librarian    | engineer   | chef | electrician |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | blues   | house         | hip-hop        |
| Sport         | basketball | water-polo | rugby         | cycling       |

