.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, card-games, magic-tricks, hiking
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, lawyer, analyst, photographer
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, russian, german, nigerian
 1. the russian is on the left or right of the chinese##3
 2. the german is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the russian##3
 4. the analyst is on the right of the german##1
 5. the german is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 7. the analyst is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the german is on the left or right of the photographer##3
 9. the chinese is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
10. the lawyer is on the left or right of the analyst##3
11. the lawyer is the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks    | baking  | card-games | hiking   |
| Job           | photographer | lawyer   | analyst    | architect |
| Nationality   | nigerian      | german | russian | chinese  |

