.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-8::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, pomegranate, nectarine, lime
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, skydiving, card-games, filmmaking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, time-travel, adventure, family
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Food          | nectarine | pomegranate    | lime | kale    |
| Hobby         | card-games     | filmmaking | skydiving  | reading |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel    | family      | drama   | adventure         |

