3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
4. the scientist is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
5. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk    | mirinda            | coffee     | almond-milk      |
| Job           | fisherman    | entrepreneur | scientist     | bartender |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | superhero    | sports | satire    |

