.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, tomato, lemon, grapes
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, disaster, family, mystery
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, polish, thai, colombian
1. the person watching family movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
3. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the polish##3
4. the person eating grapes is on the far right##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is the person eating grapes##1
6. the colombian is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
7. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the thai##1
8. the person eating tomato is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food          | tomato   | lemon | grapefruit | grapes |
| Movie-Genre   | family   | disaster     | musical      | mystery  |
| Nationality   | dutch | polish   | thai    | colombian   |

