4. the coach is on the right of the nurse##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
7. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
8. the person who's sport is basketball is the person watching disaster movies##1

