.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, water, milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, journalist, coach, firefighter
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, train, motorbike, jet-ski
1. the firefighter is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the journalist##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the coach##3
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the coach##3
6. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the train and the person drinking coffee##2
7. the person drinking iced-tea is the journalist##1
8. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Beverage    | iced-tea   | water   | coffee    | milk |
| Job         | journalist | coach    | accountant      | firefighter |
| Transport   | train      | jet-ski | motorbike | bus   |

