The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, drawing, puzzles, dancing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, motorbike, boat, roller
1. the person drinking mirinda is the person driving the bike##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person driving the roller##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
9. the person driving the boat is the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate      | mirinda | sprite       | fanta  |
| Hobby       | puzzles | sudoku | dancing    | drawing |
| Transport   | motorbike     | bike         | boat | roller     |

