4. the owner of the rabbit is between the mechanic and the american##2
5. the mechanic is the indian##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the indian##3
7. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
8. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the teacher##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |      3       |     4      |
