.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, hiking, cooking, collecting
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, quad-bike, bus, helicopter
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking cola is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the bus##2
5. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate   | iced-tea    | cola      | fanta |
| Hobby       | writing  | hiking | collecting | cooking     |
| Transport   | roller | quad-bike        | bus  | helicopter        |

