5. the japanese is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
6. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the chinese##1
7. the person drinking cola is the spanish##1
8. the person eating cucumber is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking coffee##2

.:: Answer ::.
