.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, apple, nectarine, apricot
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, social-worker, firefighter, engineer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, rowing, lacrosse, volleyball
1. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the musician##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person eating apricot##1
4. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating apple##1
5. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person eating mango and the person eating nectarine##2
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the engineer##3
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far right##1
8. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the firefighter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Food    | nectarine | apple  | mango  | apricot           |
| Job     | musician | firefighter | social-worker   | engineer |
| Sport   | volleyball   | rowing       | soccer | lacrosse  |

 